'''圣彼得和圣保罗教堂'''（St. Peter and St. Paul's Church），通常称为'''布特罗斯教堂'''（El-Botroseya），<ref name="EgyIndep Feb 17">{{cite web | url=http://www.egyptindependent.com/news/boutros-ghali-be-buried-family-s-italian-style-church | title=Boutros-Ghali to be buried at family's Italian-style church | publisher=''Egypt Independent'' | date=2016-02-17 | accessdate=2016-12-14 | archive-date=2017-01-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116193144/http://www.egyptindependent.com//news/boutros-ghali-be-buried-family-s-italian-style-church | dead-url=no }}</ref>是一个[[亚历山大科普特正教会|亚历山大科普特正教会]]小教堂，位于[[开罗|开罗]][[阿巴西亚|阿巴西亚]]区的[[科普特正教会圣马可主教座堂_(开罗)|科普特正教会圣马可主教座堂]]附近。

==历史==
该堂建于1911年，在遇刺的埃及总理布特罗斯·加利（1908-1910）的坟墓上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/251801.aspx|title=23 killed in explosion inside church attached to Cairo's Coptic cathedral|publisher=''Ahram Online''|date=11 December 2016|accessdate=2016-12-13|author=El-Mahdawy, Hadeer|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108173504/http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/251801.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>该建筑的建设过程由加利家族监督。<ref name="EgyIndep Dec 12">{{cite web|url=http://www.egyptindependent.com/news/botroseya-church-first-church-named-after-political-family|title=Botroseya Church, first church named after political family|publisher=''Egypt Independent''|date=2016-12-12|accessdate=2016-12-13|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116185222/http://www.egyptindependent.com//news/botroseya-church-first-church-named-after-political-family|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBCArabic">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/arabic/middleeast-38281433|title=حقائق عن الكنيسة البطرسية والكاتدرائية المرقسية في القاهرة|publisher=BBC Arabic|date=2016-12-11|accessdate=2016-12-13|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803125806/https://www.bbc.com/arabic/middleeast-38281433|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的孙子，第六任[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]]和前埃及外交部长[[布特罗斯·布特罗斯·加利|布特罗斯·布特罗斯·加利]]，也于2016年2月被埋葬在祭坛下的地窖里。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-02/19/c_135111140.htm | title=Egypt holds massive military funeral for former UN chief Boutros-Ghali | publisher=Xinhua | date=2016-02-19 | accessdate=2016-12-14 | archive-date=2017-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829074458/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-02/19/c_135111140.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBCArabic"/>该堂本名为圣彼得和圣保罗教堂，多年来一直被称为布特罗斯教堂，是第一个以一个政治家族命名的教堂。<ref name="EgyIndep Dec 12"/>

2016年12月11日，在该教堂发生一起自杀爆炸案，死者多达25人，其中大部分为妇女和儿童<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/12/11/505166587/bomb-hits-coptic-christian-church-in-cairo-killing-at-least-25|title=Bomb Hits Coptic Christian Church In Cairo, Killing At Least 25|publisher=NPR|work=NPR|date=11 December 2016|accessdate=13 December 2016|author=Chappell, BIll|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107113544/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/12/11/505166587/bomb-hits-coptic-christian-church-in-cairo-killing-at-least-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==设计==
该堂被当地历史学家认为具有较高的宗教和艺术价值。<ref name="BBCArabic"/><ref name="EgyIndep Dec 12"/>它是[[巴西利卡|巴西利卡]]风格，由帕夏指定的意大利-斯洛文尼亚籍首席建筑师Antonio Lasciac设计，长28米，宽17米。[[中殿|中殿]]和两侧走道用大理石柱分开，柱子上的意大利绘画描绘[[耶稣|耶稣]]、[[使徒|使徒]]和一些圣徒。在中央通道的尽头是一块黑色大理石板，上面是布特罗斯·加利的最后遗言。墙壁上的威尼斯马赛克，一幅描绘耶稣在[[约旦河|约旦河]]的洗礼，另一幅描绘耶稣、[[圣母玛利亚|圣母玛利亚]]和[[圣马尔谷|圣马尔谷]]。<ref name="EgyIndep Dec 12"/><ref>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com.eg/books/about/A_Coptic_Narrative_in_Egypt.html?id=HrpAjgEACAAJ&redir_esc=y | title=A Coptic Narrative in Egypt: A Biography of the Boutros-Ghali Family ''(book description)'' | publisher=I.B. Tauris | author=Boutros-Ghali, Youssef | year=2015 | isbn=9781780769394 | access-date=2016-12-24 | archive-date=2019-08-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828051555/https://books.google.com.eg/books/about/A_Coptic_Narrative_in_Egypt.html?id=HrpAjgEACAAJ&redir_esc=y | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.elwatannews.com/news/details/1670529 | title=الكنيسة البطرسية.. تاريخ 105 أعوام يناله «غدر الإرهاب» | publisher=''El Watan'' | date=2016-12-11 | accessdate=2016-12-14 | author=El-Zoghby, Salwa | archive-date=2019-08-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828051600/https://www.elwatannews.com/news/details/1670529 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

